<p>
<p>If you have any questions on getting started with the BoldGrid Post and Page Builder, please visit our <a href="https://www.boldgrid.com/support/boldgrid-post-and-page-builder/?utm_source=ppb-wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=readme&amp;utm_campaign=ppb" rel="nofollow ugc">Getting Started Guide</a>.<br />
