<li>Update: Misc notices.</li>
<li>Update: Disable backup now button.</li>
<li>Update: Prevent backup if the account is too large.</li>
</ul>
<h4>1.3.2</h4>
<p>Release Date: December 6th, 2016</p>
<ul>
