<li>Update: Improve time to calculate disk space.</li>
<li>Bug fix: Added double-quote encapsulation to the password in the mysqldump defaults file.</li>
<li>Bug fix: Typo fix.</li>
</ul>
<h4>1.3.1</h4>
<p>Release Date: November 15th, 2016</p>
