<li>Update: Modify backup success message with a link to settings.</li>
<li>Update: Modify BoldGrid Backup menus.</li>
<li>Update: Adjust display of preflight check.</li>
<li>Update: Free limitations to days of the week.</li>
<li>Update: Free limitations to retention.</li>
<li>Update: Standard tooltips.</li>
