<li><strong>Improved</strong>: Weâ€™ve added a little filter on {all_fields} shortcode. When sending email notification itâ€™s going to exclude all the empty fields. So it becomes more readable.</li>
<li><strong>Fix</strong>: There was some issue with CSV exporting. We fixed that.</li>
</ul>
<h4>Version 1.2.0 (30 October, 2017)</h4>
